text: Undercover Doctor is a 1939 American crime movie directed by Louis King and starring Lloyd Nolan, Janice Logan, J. Carrol Naish, Heather Angel, Broderick Crawford, Stanley Price, Richard Carle, Raymond Hatton, John Eldredge, George Meeker, Paul Fix, Richard Denning. It was distributed by Paramount Pictures. ==Other websites== * Category:1939 crime movies Category:American crime movies Category:Movies directed by Louis King Category:Paramount Pictures movies
